linuxdroid (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release of LinuxDroid
  * Features:
    - First-run setup wizard with 6 screens
    - Automatic Android x86 image download
    - Background download service with systemd
    - Multi-instance Android emulator support
    - KVM hardware acceleration
    - Resume capability for interrupted downloads
    - SHA256 checksum verification
    - ADB bridge support
    - System tray integration
  * Supported Android versions:
    - Android 9.0 (Pie) - Recommended
    - Android 11 (R)
    - Android 13 (Tiramisu)
  * System requirements:
    - Ubuntu 20.04+ or Debian 11+
    - KVM-enabled CPU
    - 8GB RAM minimum
    - 20GB disk space

 -- Dharun Ashokkumar <contact@tripletech.com>  Sun, 16 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000
